{"tid":2404783,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"撞車有問題（求巴絲打解答","createTime":"2021-02-12T02:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T12:06:02.000Z","uid":47288,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"607c22a8ce9cfe670eff541b93df3390e51bc0b2","tid":2404783,"uid":47288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我先貼事發地點，怕我畫得唔清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事發地點如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVyYC7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVyYC7K.jpg&h=b49077f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xchnkqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxchnkqk.jpg&h=50139c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時我就係中線行緊嘅（笑哈哈個架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），個陣離三四個車位見到左線有架車打住左燈慢駛（大約3/4km/h)，最後仲要停埋係我所標記嘅位置，咁我以為佢係要停係到所以當佢係死車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnBvuep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnBvuep.jpg&h=3263f410&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁因為個陣我就要轉左入小路，而個條小路係容納到兩個車位嘅，咁我就係中線直接轉左，個陣我見條路除咗我同果架車之外，只有一輛巴士跟住我後面，咁我冇行到最左線轉入去（因為以為果架係死車）<br />\n同埋我轉入去時冇攞到最右，反而係左轆踩住中間線轉入去<br />\n當我轉到入去時個架打燈嘅車忽然隊我車尾轆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGv4yF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGv4yF4.gif&h=57ef6203&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住就話我轉入去踩咗佢條線先會撞到，仲要話我冇打燈轉入去（但我其實有打）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就想問下巴絲打，咁究竟呢單野係誰對誰錯呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(ps.好彩嘅係我架車冇撞爛任何野，連少少花都見唔到，但佢就撞到車頭bumper就快甩咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f550733f5f39f48512e9c23791101012fe5b3778","tid":2404783,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"有冇車cam"},{"pid":"59fb8498d54cee920857263fadcecc9116d801a6","tid":2404783,"uid":47288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f550733f5f39f48512e9c23791101012fe5b3778","tid":2404783,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"有冇車cam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"我有，但對家車唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317e357abadbdba36984e617cc2e6474845856bc","tid":2404783,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fb8498d54cee920857263fadcecc9116d801a6","tid":2404783,"uid":47288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f550733f5f39f48512e9c23791101012fe5b3778","tid":2404783,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"有冇車cam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"我有，但對家車唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:53:32.000Z","msg":"你有車cam片，交通部信你就得。"},{"pid":"e99fdca83c946a2b7527100f2d70c2eb706abf8d","tid":2404783,"uid":47288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317e357abadbdba36984e617cc2e6474845856bc","tid":2404783,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fb8498d54cee920857263fadcecc9116d801a6","